---
const questions = [
  {
    question: "Who is eligible to apply?",
    answer:'Everyone is welcome to apply, but you need to qualified with the roles provided.'
  },
  {
    question: "What can I do to get benefits?",
    answer:'The benefits you can get is depends on your rank. It can be $DEV, get along with our partners project, and builders swag.'
  },
  {
    question: "What are the roles?",
    answer:'We have provided three roles for Developers, Marketing, Technical Content Writers.'
  },
  {
    question: "How much time do I need to commit?",
    answer:'The program is flexible, it\'s up in your free time but the more you invest your time in Dev Protocol, the more opportunity you can get.'
  },
  {
    question: "When the applications open?",
    answer:'Application to the program is open from December 20th to January 20th. The application remains open for a month and you can apply once every application cycle opens.'
  },

]
---
<section
  class="
    p-5 my-6 md:-mt-10
  "
>
  <div class="w-auto items-center flex flex-col space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1 mx-8 sm:mx-16 space-y-2">
        <h4 class="font-semibold font-display text-3xl leading-relaxed">Frequently asked questions</h4>
        <p>Can’t find the answer you’re looking for? Reach out to our <a href="https://discord.gg/VwJp4KM" class="underline hover:text-blue-600">support</a> team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1 space-y-6 flex flex-col mx-8 sm:mx-16 pt-4">
        {questions.map(item=>(
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">{item.question}</h4>
                <p>{item.answer}</p>
            </div>
        ))}
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>
